@startuml
title <font size=12>Kelola Data Barang - Admin</font>

actor Admin
participant "View List" as View
participant "Controller" as Controller
participant "Database" as Database

== View Data ==
Admin->View: Akses halaman data barang
View->Controller: GET /admin/barang
Controller->Database: Query semua barang
Database-->Controller: Return daftar barang
Controller-->View: Tampilkan tabel barang
View-->Admin: Display list dengan action buttons

== Create Barang ==
Admin->View: Klik tombol tambah barang
View->Controller: Tampilkan form create
Controller-->View: Display form kosong
Admin->View: Isi data barang baru
View->Controller: POST /admin/barang\n(nama, kategori, harga_beli, harga_jual, stok, satuan)
Controller->Controller: Validate data
Controller->Database: Create barang baru
Database-->Controller: Return success
Controller-->View: Redirect ke list
View-->Admin: Display success message

== Update Barang ==
Admin->View: Klik tombol edit barang
View->Controller: GET /admin/barang/{id}/edit
Controller->Database: Query barang by ID
Database-->Controller: Return barang data
Controller-->View: Display form dengan data lama
Admin->View: Ubah data barang
View->Controller: PUT /admin/barang/{id}\n(nama, kategori, harga_beli, harga_jual, stok, satuan)
Controller->Controller: Validate data
Controller->Database: Update barang
Database-->Controller: Return success
Controller-->View: Redirect ke list
View-->Admin: Display success message

== Delete Barang ==
Admin->View: Klik tombol hapus barang
View->Controller: DELETE /admin/barang/{id}
Controller->Database: Query barang by ID
Database-->Controller: Return barang
Controller->Database: Delete barang
Database-->Controller: Return success
Controller-->View: Redirect ke list
View-->Admin: Display success message

@enduml
